      "content": "I get that, but it feels like there's a difference. Like, some people use it to attack actual facts and reporting, while others just use it as a shield to ignore things that are true but inconvenient. Do you think one side is using the term more \"dishonestly\" than the other to delegitimize actual journalism?",
